Discontinued Transcription

 

Transcription Regulatory Sequence (TRS)

The nested subgenomic transcription produces different subgenomic RNA (sgRNA) species.

The process is mediated by the TRS () which bring the 5' end of the RNA in proximity with the start codon of downstream ORF.

Long-Read Workshop 2021  PMID: 32330414 Kim et al.,  bioRxiv 2021.02.06.430041

Take-Home Messages

  Sequencing provides read out of single nucleotide and structural variants

  Long-read sequencing enables phasing of nucleotide and structural variants

  Long-reads illuminates the facets of Sar-CoV-2 plasticity
